-- Sony to keep pursuing network strategies after security breach
-- 
-- Tue May 3, 2011 2:12am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/05/03/us-sony-network-idUSTRE7400K920110503

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Sony Corp will continue to build its network-related businesses as a key strategy for the company, Executive Deputy President Kazuo Hirai told a news conference on Sunday held to address the massive security breach of its PlayStation Network. 

 (Reporting by  Isabel Reynolds ; Editing by  Nathan Layne )